    <subsubsection>
      <title><xref ref="exer_prove_onto_finite_discrete"></xref> Select Answers and Hints</title>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <p>
            <m>f(0)=</m> even and <m>f(1)=</m> odd.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
